    <P>We are strict guidelines to follow all of the State and Local mandates, as well as those imposed by the state board of barbering and cosmetology.

    There are no exceptions to the following rules:
    
    -If you or any member of your household have recently had any symptoms of sickness, we kindly ask you reschedule your appointment for a future date.
    -When you arrive please have a mask on when entering the salon and we will check your temperature prior to your appointment. You are required to wear a mask for the entirety of your appointment. This rule also applies to staff members. If you do not have a mask, a disposable one will be provided for you.
