    <p>I cherish your time and believe your appointment time is extremely valuable. I hold your appointment time specifically for you. If you must cancel or reschedule your appointment, I kindly ask you give a 24-hour notice. Any cancellations given less than a 24-hour notice will be charged 50% of the service(s) with a minimum $30 charge. All No Shows will be charged 100% of service(s). I understand some circumstances are unforeseen and I will show grace where possible, but please remember this is my livelihood when asking for exceptions.
